     DESAI, J.	I broadly agree with the conclusion recorded
by my brother.
     The learned  Judge in  deciding the  S.L.P. (Crl)	Nos.
1149-50/1984 has  followed the	decision of  this Court. The
learned Judge  was perfectly justified and indeed it was the
duty of	 the learned  Judge to	follow the  decision of this
Court which is binding on him.
     Special leave petitions are dismissed.
H.S.K.					Petitions dismissed.
